Author: paperklipp
Text: > my ed was speaking through me  This is so real. When I’m deep in a restriction phase and my brain fog is thick, the only thing I can engage in conversation about is food, it’s the only thing my mind can focus on for longer than four seconds. I can talk and talk and talk about it and as soon as somebody introduces another topic I shut down because I can’t think about anything else. I’ve never thought of it as my ed “speaking through” me before but that’s a great way of describing it.

Author: lightningmcqueef69
Text: this is truly so goddamn inspiring and i wish you the absolute best of luck. you got this, and we're all here if you need support ❤
